data.description: If these COVID times call for a beautifully updated home on a greenbelt with room for your home office, remote learning areas for kids, exercise room, game room for recreating and gorgeous neighborhood with pool/park/tennis, then LOOK NO FURTHER! Spacious master down w/2 walk-in closets & tastefully updated bath w/ separate vanities & waterfall shower. Wood floors on main level, stairs & upstairs game room. Kitchen upgrades include oversized island w/ Bosch gas cooking, built-in Bosch oven, new granite, backsplash & sink, pantry glass door, stainless steel appliances. Plantation Shutters array all windows down & added crown molding. 4 bedrooms upstairs to utilize as you wish plus huge game room. Plentiful closet space. Extra storage under stairs. Vivint doorbell/cameras will stay. Easy access to 1604 & 151. Nearby shopping & entertainment.
